Package: sfd-tool
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libgtk-3-0,
         libusb-1.0-0,
         imagemagick
Description: Serial Flash Device Programming Tool
 A cross-platform GTK3 application for programming serial flash devices.
 Features:
  * Support for various flash chip types
  * USB-based programming interface
  * Both graphical (GTK) and command-line interfaces
  * Cross-platform support (Linux, Windows, macOS)
 .
 This tool is useful for embedded developers and electronics hobbyists
 who need to program SPI flash chips.
